- 命中 - 海豚大挪移
- You got me. - Dolphin style retreat!

333
00:21:30,790 --> 00:21:33,050
準備好了 兒子
Go long son.

334
00:21:33,660 --> 00:21:36,510
我還沒準備好呢
I wasn't ready.

335
00:21:36,890 --> 00:21:38,430
- 接好了 - 接住了
- Coming back at you. - I got it.

336
00:21:38,440 --> 00:21:41,460
- 往上拋 - 來了 接好了
- Throw it high! - Here you go. Yeah, C'mon.

337
00:21:42,200 --> 00:21:45,980
- 我要來了 - 那就來吧 犀牛大師
- I'm coming for you. - Bring it on Master Rhino.

338
00:21:45,990 --> 00:21:47,570
我來了
Here I come!

339
00:21:56,390 --> 00:21:59,070
我要追上你了 追上你
I'm gonna get you. I'm gonna get you.

340
00:21:59,090 --> 00:22:03,160
追上你
I'm gonna get you.

341
00:22:03,190 --> 00:22:04,450
停停停
Shh, stop.

342
00:22:04,470 --> 00:22:08,900
誰會追上你 誰追上你了
Who's gonna get you? Who's gonna get you?

343
00:22:10,610 --> 00:22:14,740
- 犀牛大師 - 怎麼 怎麼了
- Master Rhino. - Why, what's wrong?

344
00:22:20,240 --> 00:22:21,810
你們好
Hello.

345
00:22:22,370 --> 00:22:25,480
大夥 你們永遠也猜不到他是誰
Guys guys, you're never gonna guess who just showed up.

346
00:22:25,480 --> 00:22:26,810
不會一輩子也猜不到
Not in a million years.

347
00:22:26,810 --> 00:22:28,820
只是你們不可能... 你們猜猜
You can't.... you just try.

348
00:22:28,840 --> 00:22:29,850
- 你爸爸 - 你爸爸
- Your father! - Your father!

349
00:22:29,880 --> 00:22:31,690
怎麼都一猜就中
Wow, how did you just guess that?

350
00:22:31,720 --> 00:22:34,230
好吧 當然會猜到 我們看起來簡直一模一樣
Oh, wait a second. Yeah of course. We look exactly the same.

351
00:22:34,240 --> 00:22:36,370
老爸 跟我朋友打聲招呼吧
Dad. Say hi to my friends,

352
00:22:36,370 --> 00:22:39,320
這是螳螂 嬌虎 金猴 仙鶴 還有靈蛇
Mantis, Tigress, Monkey, Crane, and Viper.

353
00:22:39,340 --> 00:22:41,370
- 你是靈蛇 對嗎 - 我是金猴 大叔
- Oh, Viper, was it? - Monkey, sir.

354
00:22:41,400 --> 00:22:42,960
他們是我最好的朋友
They're kind of my best friends.

355
00:22:42,970 --> 00:22:46,900
這...這位是師傅 他是個傳奇
And this... this is Master Shifu. Legend.

356
00:22:46,930 --> 00:22:49,840
很榮幸見到你 熊貓大師
It is an honor to meet you, Master Panda.

357
00:22:49,870 --> 00:22:52,880
或許你爸爸願意隨我們一起到練功房
Perhaps your father would care to join us in the training hall?

358
00:22:52,910 --> 00:22:55,570
您兒子要給他們上課
Your son will be teaching the class.

359
00:22:56,710 --> 00:22:58,890
他肯定很累 你一定很累
I'm sure he's tired. I'm sure you're tired.

360
00:22:58,890 --> 00:23:01,210
他累了 我帶他去菊花房休息
He's tired. I'm gonna show him the chrysanthemums suite.

361
00:23:01,240 --> 00:23:04,790
什麼 累 不 一定也不累 我很想看你教課
What? Tired? No, I'm fine. I would love to watch you teach.

362
00:23:04,800 --> 00:23:07,010
相信我 看我教課一點也不有趣...
Trust me. It would be more fun to watch me...

363
00:23:07,040 --> 00:23:08,990
- 戰斗 - 那是什麼
- Fight! - What is that?

364
00:23:09,020 --> 00:23:11,060
村子被人攻擊了
The valley is under attack.

365
00:23:11,790 --> 00:23:14,500
- 兒子 被攻擊 - 這太棒了
- Son? Under attack? -This is perfect!

366
00:23:14,510 --> 00:23:17,650
這下你就要見識神龍大俠的厲害了
Now you can see what being the dragon warrior is all about.

367
00:23:17,660 --> 00:23:19,380
跟我來
Follow me!

368
00:23:25,760 --> 00:23:29,130
你們這群惡徒 準備...
Enemies of justice. Prepare for....

369
00:23:29,140 --> 00:23:31,610
開什麼玩笑
Are you kidding me?

370
00:23:33,500 --> 00:23:34,780
痛
Ow!

371
00:23:39,900 --> 00:23:42,300
這些綠家夥是什麼玩意兒
What's the deal with the green guys?

372
00:23:42,320 --> 00:23:45,790
- 某種翡翠僵屍 - 翡翠僵屍
- Some kind of jade zombies. - Jade zombies?

373
00:23:45,820 --> 00:23:47,700
- 翡屍 就是這個 - 翡屍 就是這個
- Jombies, Jinx. - Jombies, Jinx.

374
00:23:48,920 --> 00:23:50,450
小蓮花 小心點
- Lotus, be careful!

375
00:23:50,450 --> 00:23:53,220
爸 沒事 這事我每天都在做...
- It's Okay, Dad. I do this everyday...!

376
00:23:54,550 --> 00:23:58,120
我認識他們 他們是雙獾大師
I recognize this guys. The Master Badger twins.

377
00:23:58,130 --> 00:24:01,050
和他們的雙擊絕招
With their crushing double gong technique.

378
00:24:01,070 --> 00:24:04,820
對 就是這個 那個是...不是吧
Yeah, that's the one. That guys is.... no

379
00:24:04,840 --> 00:24:07,060
豪豬大師
Master Porcupine.

380
00:24:09,480 --> 00:24:11,790
他不是幾百年前就去世了嗎
I thought he died hundred years ago?

381
00:24:11,820 --> 00:24:13,880
全是傳奇人物
These guys are legends.

382
00:24:13,900 --> 00:24:15,940
來張速寫
Get a quick sketch of us.

383
00:24:22,900 --> 00:24:24,650
畫好了嗎 畫好了嗎
Did you get it? Did you get it?

384
00:24:24,680 --> 00:24:28,030
我眨眼了 能再畫一張嗎
I blinked. Can we get another one?

385
00:24:30,470 --> 00:24:34,630
我要被豪豬大師掐死了 簡直太帥了
I'm being choked by Master Porcupine. This is so cool.

386
00:24:35,900 --> 00:24:38,550
- 看 是你 - 阿寶 專心點
- Look. It's you. - Po, focus!

387
00:24:38,560 --> 00:24:42,940
宇宙消息 那我再來給你條宇宙消息吧
Message from the universe. I'll give you one message from the universe...

388
00:24:42,970 --> 00:24:45,180
離我兒子遠點
Stay away from my son.

389
00:24:45,580 --> 00:24:46,970
抱歉 爸 稍後我會清幹凈
Sorry dad. I'll clean it up later.

390
00:24:47,000 --> 00:24:50,100
小心點 別用我的好鍋 用這個
Whoa, whoa, not my good pan. Take this one.

391
00:24:52,140 --> 00:24:54,300
小蓮花小心
Lotus, watch out!

392
00:24:58,780 --> 00:25:01,150
老爸 看我的無敵連環包
Dad, check out my dumplings of doom.

393
00:25:11,970 --> 00:25:13,560
抓到了
Gotcha!

394
00:25:17,760 --> 00:25:19,910
我看見你們了
I see you.

395
00:25:19,930 --> 00:25:22,680
你們的氣很快就是我的了
Your chi will soon be mine.

396
00:25:22,700 --> 00:25:25,070
- 他在跟我說話嗎 - 哪個 他們三個都在說話
- Is he talking to me? - Which one? They're all talking.

397
00:25:25,100 --> 00:25:27,220
對 太恐怖了
You're right. That's so scary.

398
00:25:27,230 --> 00:25:29,610
我們應該也要試試看 說不定能反過來嚇唬他們
We should try that, too. Maybe it'd be scary back at them.

399
00:25:29,620 --> 00:25:31,190
好 不過我們得先商量好應該怎麼說
Okay, but we gotta plan what we're gonna say first,

400
00:25:31,210 --> 00:25:33,010
要不然的話 那就不是可怕了 而是蠢了
otherwise it won't be scary, it'll be just stupid.

401
00:25:33,030 --> 00:25:35,530
不是他們在說話 白癡
It's not them talking, you idiots!

402
00:25:35,540 --> 00:25:37,950
是我在通過他們說話 我是天煞
It's me talking through them, Kai!

403
00:25:37,980 --> 00:25:41,040
- 誰 - 好好 夠了
- Who? - Okay, okay, enough.

404
00:25:47,030 --> 00:25:48,680
- 看到了嗎 看到了嗎 - 發生了什麼
- Did you see that? Did you see? - What just happened?

405
00:25:48,700 --> 00:25:51,170
那些綠煙就咻的一下 又咻地消失了
The green smoke just poof.... and then poof.

406
00:25:51,200 --> 00:25:52,600
師傅 那是什麼
Shifu, what wast that?

407
00:25:52,630 --> 00:25:55,870
天煞 天煞 天煞 是誰呢
Kai? Kai? Kai?

408
00:25:56,010 --> 00:25:58,010
不知道 沒聽過
Nope. Never heard of him.

409
00:25:58,030 --> 00:26:00,830
天煞 天煞 在哪
Kai... Kai... Where is it?

410
00:26:00,860 --> 00:26:03,690
這堣茼h裝滿智慧的卷軸了 什麼都找不到
There's so much wisdom in here, I can't find anything.

411
00:26:03,710 --> 00:26:05,130
找到了
Yes!

412
00:26:05,780 --> 00:26:07,530
看好了
Behold.

413
00:26:08,540 --> 00:26:11,520
所有答案都將在這塈鋮
All the answers will be found within.

414
00:26:13,200 --> 00:26:16,140
什麼 一片空白
What? It's blank?

415
00:26:16,150 --> 00:26:19,460
是在耍我嗎 又來這套
Are you kidding me? Not again.

416
00:26:20,450 --> 00:26:25,220
等等 等一下 抱歉 好了 我們開始吧
Wait, wait. Hold on. Sorry, okay, here we go.

417
00:26:25,650 --> 00:26:28,410
是烏龜親手寫的
It is written in Oogway's hand.

418
00:26:28,440 --> 00:26:32,410
- 很久以前 我有一個兄弟 - 烏龜竟然有兄弟
- Long ago, I had a brother. - Oogway had a brother?

419
00:26:32,440 --> 00:26:34,470
戰友 是戰友 抱歉
In arms. In arms, sorry.

420
00:26:34,480 --> 00:26:36,290
他寫的是兄弟般的戰友
- He says brother in arms.

421
00:26:36,290 --> 00:26:38,240
你就不能一次性展開卷軸嗎
- Can't you just unroll it all at once?

422
00:26:39,220 --> 00:26:44,020
我曾是一名雄心勃勃的年輕戰士 帶領一支偉大的軍隊
I was an ambitious young warrior leading a great army.

423
00:26:45,730 --> 00:26:48,870
與我並肩作戰的就是天煞
And fighting by my side was Kai.

424
00:26:49,260 --> 00:26:51,820
我最親密的朋友
My closest friend.

425
00:26:54,240 --> 00:26:59,080
有一天 我們遭到了埋伏 我身負重傷
One day we were ambushed. I was badly wounded.

426
00:26:59,090 --> 00:27:04,170
我的朋友背著我日以繼夜地尋求幫助
My friend carried me for days looking for help.

427
00:27:04,180 --> 00:27:08,960
最後我們來到一個高山上的神秘村莊
Until we came to a secret village, high in the mountains.

428
00:27:08,990 --> 00:27:12,070
古老的療傷聖地
An ancient place of healing.

429
00:27:12,080 --> 00:27:15,640
全村都是熊貓
A village of pandas.

430
00:27:15,650 --> 00:27:19,040
- 熊貓 - 對 熊貓
- Pandas? - Yes, pandas.

431
00:27:19,060 --> 00:27:24,040
熊貓他們用氣功治好了我
Pandas who used the power of chi to heal me.

432
00:27:26,520 --> 00:27:30,320
他們還教會我如何釋放氣
They taught me how to give chi.

433
00:27:33,240 --> 00:27:39,490
但天煞想獨占所有氣
But Kai, wanted the power all to himself.

434
00:27:39,510 --> 00:27:44,730
他發現氣既能被給予 也能被奪走
He saw that what could be given could also be taken.

435
00:27:47,810 --> 00:27:50,980
我必須阻止他
I had to stop him.

436
00:27:54,720 --> 00:27:57,740
我們打得山搖地動
Our battle shook the Earth.

437
00:27:57,750 --> 00:28:03,010
最終 我將他打入靈界
Until, finally, I banished Kai to the Spirit Realm.

438
00:28:03,020 --> 00:28:05,820
若他重返人間
Should he ever return to the mortal realm,

439
00:28:05,830 --> 00:28:10,140
唯有真正的氣功大師才能阻止他
he can only be stopped by a true Master of chi.

440
00:28:10,170 --> 00:28:13,070
真正的氣功大師 比如你
True Master of chi? Like you.

441
00:28:13,100 --> 00:28:15,200
我 我只能發功讓花盛開而已
Me? I can barely make a flower bloom!

442
00:28:15,210 --> 00:28:17,650
我至少還要在山洞堶袚狺T十年
I'd need at least thirty more years, and a cave.

443
00:28:17,660 --> 00:28:19,200
我們需要一個氣功大師
We need a chi Master.

444
00:28:19,230 --> 00:28:23,320
他會繼續奪走別的大師的氣 世上就再也沒氣了
He will continue stealing the chi of Masters until he has consumed it all.

445
00:28:23,340 --> 00:28:24,360
我們必須想辦法阻止他
We have to make a way to stop him.

446
00:28:24,370 --> 00:28:27,180
敗下的大師越多 他得到的氣也就越多
He gets more more powerful with every Master he defeats.

447
00:28:27,200 --> 00:28:28,840
我們沒別的選擇 只能去戰斗
There is no choice. We fight.

448
00:28:28,860 --> 00:28:31,180
我可以教你 兒子
I can teach you, son.

449
00:28:31,870 --> 00:28:37,590
- 你可以教我 - 當然 我是只熊貓
- You can do this? - Of course, I'm a panda.

450
00:28:37,610 --> 00:28:40,680
這肯定是宇宙讓你來的原因
That must be why the universe sent you here.

451
00:28:40,690 --> 00:28:43,000
好 那我要做什麼
Okay, so what do I have to do?

452
00:28:43,020 --> 00:28:45,920
- 你要跟我回家 - 什麼
- You have to come home with me. - What?

453
00:28:45,950 --> 00:28:48,610
- 回到神秘村莊 - 對 兒子
- To the secret village? - Yes, son.

454
00:28:48,630 --> 00:28:52,540
你必須重新學會如何做一只熊貓
You must rediscover what it is to be a panda.

455
00:28:52,570 --> 00:28:56,230
你要學會如何像熊貓那樣生活 像熊貓那樣睡覺
You have to learn how to live like a panda. Sleep like a panda.

456
00:28:56,260 --> 00:28:58,810
像熊貓那樣吃東西
Eat like a panda.

457
00:28:58,840 --> 00:29:03,560
103個包子 還沒夠我塞牙縫呢
Those 103 dumplings? I was just warming up.

458
00:29:03,590 --> 00:29:07,200
我一直認為 我吃東西的潛力還沒全部挖掘出來
I've always felt like I wasn't eating up to my full potential.

459
00:29:07,210 --> 00:29:11,640
你不能把我們家阿寶帶走 不不 我要別的意見
You can't take Po away from me. No, no I want a second opinion.

460
00:29:11,650 --> 00:29:14,450
師傅 再開一卷吧
Shifu, open another scroll or something.

461
00:29:14,460 --> 00:29:17,600
- 我覺得他應該去 - 好 再來個意見
- I think he should go. - Fine. A third opinion.

462
00:29:17,620 --> 00:29:20,060
金猴 靈蛇 嬌虎
Monkey? Viper? Tigress?

463
00:29:20,080 --> 00:29:22,920
老爸 你也聽到師傅說的和烏龜寫的
Dad, you heard what Shifu said, Oogway said.

464
00:29:22,950 --> 00:29:25,590
只有真正的氣功大師才能阻止天煞
This guy can only be stopped by a Master of chi.

465
00:29:25,600 --> 00:29:29,310
而我只有知道我究竟是誰才能學會用氣
And I can only master chi by knowing who I really am.

466
00:29:29,320 --> 00:29:32,200
我 我是熊貓
Well, I'm a panda.

467
00:29:35,710 --> 00:29:38,820
我去給你準備路上的午餐
I'll pack your lunch for the road.

468
00:29:44,120 --> 00:29:47,220
你真的認為阿寶能及時學會氣功嗎
Do you really think Po can master chi in time?

469
00:29:47,250 --> 00:29:48,930
我的想法並不重要
Doesn't matter what I think.

470
00:29:48,940 --> 00:29:53,180
- 宇宙怎麼想才是最重要的 - 所以答案是不會
- It only matters what the universe thinks. - So, that's a "No"?

471
00:29:53,190 --> 00:29:56,930
- 師傅 我們要做什麼 - 你去查明天煞的下落
- Master, what are we going to do? - You are going to find out where Kai is.

472
00:29:56,940 --> 00:30:00,350
尋著那些翡翠僵屍的蹤跡 但千萬別跟他打起來
Follow the trail of those jade creatures but do not engage.

473
00:30:00,360 --> 00:30:04,020
因為天煞會越戰越強
For with every foe he faces Kai becomes stronger.

474
00:30:04,030 --> 00:30:06,670
為什麼選我 是因為我多嘴嗎
- Why me? Is it because I asked.

475
00:30:06,670 --> 00:30:08,320
不是 因為你能飛
- No, it is because you can fly.

476
00:30:08,330 --> 00:30:11,930
- 去吧 - 早知道就閉上你的鳥嘴了
- Go! - Should have kept your beak shut.

477
00:30:11,940 --> 00:30:14,570
- 帶上螳螂 - 什麼 因為我插嘴...
- And take Mantis. - What? Oh man, is it because I ...?

478
00:30:14,590 --> 00:30:15,810
對
Yes.

479
00:30:42,290 --> 00:30:44,740
吃點東西嗎
Oh, lunch break?

480
00:30:44,760 --> 00:30:47,170
你不用同樣問題問兩遍
You don't need to ask me twice.

481
00:30:47,200 --> 00:30:49,170
- 老爸 - 幹嘛
- Dad? - Yes?

482
00:30:49,190 --> 00:30:51,130
- 老爸 - 啥
- Dad? - Yes?

483
00:30:51,140 --> 00:30:52,720
你在這媟F什麼
- What are you doing here?

484
00:30:52,720 --> 00:30:55,110
你說我在幹什麼 我背疼死了
- What am I doing? Getting a backache.

485
00:30:55,120 --> 00:30:57,080
你非得在每塊石頭上踩著走嗎
Did you have to step on every rock?

486
00:30:57,090 --> 00:31:00,610
- 不 我是說你怎麼在這 - 那你說我該怎麼辦
- No, I mean why are you here? - What was I supposed to do?

487
00:31:00,620 --> 00:31:02,820
如果你不喜歡吃那些熊貓的東西怎麼辦
What if the pandas don't have food you like?

488
00:31:02,830 --> 00:31:06,870
你餓著肚子的話 怎麼去拯救世界呀
